<template>
        <v-toolbar dark color="#3b5998" dense>
            <v-toolbar-title>NAVEGAÇÃO</v-toolbar-title>

            <v-icon>clear</v-icon>
            </v-btn>

<style>
</style>

<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            toggle_exclusive: 0
        }
    },
    methods: {
        mudaPagina(novaPagina) {
            this.$emit('mudarPagina', novaPagina)
        }
    }
}
</script>
